WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:01.933
These flowers are blooming so beautifully.

2
00:00:01.933 --> 00:00:04.500
We don’t have such delicate flowers in Loulan.

3
00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:08.066
Aren’t they beautiful? Mm, yes.

4
00:00:16.933 --> 00:00:19.400
I’ll have the Song family avenge you.

5
00:00:33.866 --> 00:00:34.966
Ah, ah!

6
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:36.166
How did you get out?

7
00:00:36.166 --> 00:00:37.500
Xiu Dao, An Qi, let go of me!

8
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:39.200
I miss the quiet before.

9
00:00:43.800 --> 00:00:46.100
Someone, take the princess to the Imperial Hospital!

10
00:00:52.666 --> 00:00:55.266
Is everything alright? I heard you were in the Imperial Garden.

11
00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:57.033
I was so frightened!

12
00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:58.266
I’m fine.

13
00:00:58.266 --> 00:00:59.800
It was just that the Loulan princess was accidentally injured.

14
00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:02.666
I sent her to the Imperial Hospital for treatment.

15
00:01:02.866 --> 00:01:04.466
And you? Are you hurt?

16
00:01:04.466 --> 00:01:05.800
Your Majesty, don’t worry.

17
00:01:05.933 --> 00:01:08.366
I was wearing a Diamond Armor in advance.

18
00:01:08.366 --> 00:01:09.600
It’s impervious to blades and bullets.

19
00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:12.466
I didn’t expect a minor accident to occur.

20
00:01:12.566 --> 00:01:15.466
The Loulan princess suddenly rushed out and shielded me.

21
00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:18.500
This is absurd. I had known someone would try to assassinate.

22
00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:20.400
Then why didn’t you tell me?

23
00:01:20.766 --> 00:01:22.433
What if something happened?

24
00:01:22.466 --> 00:01:24.300
I didn’t want to make you worry.

25
00:01:24.466 --> 00:01:27.100
Even if Your Majesty would send many people to protect me,

26
00:01:27.266 --> 00:01:30.366
I was just afraid of alarming the enemy.

27
00:01:32.500 --> 00:01:35.133
Your Majesty, don’t be angry.

28
00:01:35.133 --> 00:01:37.400
I’ve made thorough preparations.

29
00:01:37.666 --> 00:01:39.400
Anger is harmful to health.

30
00:01:42.066 --> 00:01:44.700
By the way, how is the Empress Dowager?

31
00:01:44.700 --> 00:01:46.300
Consort De was captured on the spot.

32
00:01:46.766 --> 00:01:49.466
Report to Your Majesty, her hand contained a deadly poison.

33
00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:51.466
Now the only thing that can save her,

34
00:01:51.466 --> 00:01:53.933
is probably the Wan Jin Dan that Loulan offered two years ago.

35
00:01:53.933 --> 00:01:56.133
It’s the antidote for all poisons.

36
00:01:56.133 --> 00:01:58.433
Li Zhongguan, go get it quickly!
